survey_response.review_text: I visited Dr. Pannam in the second trimester of my pregnancy, after reading the reviews and delivered my first baby with her in July 2023. From the very first meeting I could feel so much connected and comfortable with her. She listens to every tiny detail that the expecting parents want to share or the questions they want to ask and then responds to everything in a very calm, friendly and loving manner. I guess that’s the most important thing that every pregnant woman looks for in her doctor. Also, she gives a very straightforward and clear advice, and will not misguide or please you just for the sake of money. Definitely recommend to everyone.

Last year, we embarked on our healthcare journey with Dr. Pannam, and from the very beginning, she has played a crucial role in guiding us through the various stages of my maternity experience. Her support and expertise extended from preconception counseling right through to the safe delivery of our baby. Dr. Pannam consistently ensured that we were well-informed about each step of the process, and her dedication to our care left us completely satisfied with the high standard of service she provided. Her professionalism and compassionate nature made a significant impact on us, and we are confident that anyone seeking a doctor for similar reasons would benefit greatly from her exceptional care.
Ample time was spent during consultation and regular followup with guidance . I felt at ease while communicating with the doctor . Doctor was always available on call.

Dr.Pannam Sharma is a great doctor..she is very friendly with the patients..she guided me very well through both my pregnancies and catered to all my queries patiently..she answered all my questions and explained me treatment process thoroughly..
I would recommend Dr.Pannam Sharma to all the ladies willing for a satisfactory treatment…

We want to express our most heartfelt gratitude to Dr. Pannam for taking such good care of us during the pregnancy as well as the delivery!! Because of her great knowledge and great smiles, we felt certain like we were in good hands and that gave us peace of mind towards the big day.

It was her remarkable experience and skill that could identify the potential complications that could have arisen and hence the delivery was planned at the right time. After suffering from infertility issues over last many years, we felt truly blessed to be under her and Dr. Arvind' care. Their team work has been very reassuring. 

We were referred to her around 24th week by Dr. Arvind Vaid to take our care during the last stages of pregnancy with plans of delivery at Apollo Cradle, Moti Nagar. Their guidance and professionalism have brought a miracle into our lives after 10 years of marriage when we had lost all hopes.

We will forever be grateful to you!

Best regards, 
Dipti and Tarun
